        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3141656064" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7047864252376447713">This collection of short stories orbits the topics of death, connection, memory and stories. I learned quite a few new word to me. For instance: disquisition, condign and extrications. Those words can be found in pages 11 and 14. I stopped recording the rest, because it was making for slow going. Words unknown to me were peppered throughout the texts.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


